			(property "Description" "Potentiometer (Pot)\n\nThree-terminal potentiometers, with an adjustable wiper and two adjustable resistors. A pot can be used to create a configurable voltage divider, or as a variable resistor.\n\nVariants ALPS_POT and ALPS_POT_KIT - PTH, breadboard compatible, 9mm square pots\n\n• https://www.sparkfun.com/products/9288 Rotary Potentiometer - Linear (10k ohm) (COM-09288)\n• The KIT variant exposes copper on only one side of the PTH pad, so the part can only be assembled on one side of the PCB. Useful for beginner soldering kits."
				(at 0 0 0)
				(effects
					(font
						(size 1.27 1.27)
					)
					(hide yes)
				)
			)
